snippet.title: Trailer - METAVOIDAL
snippet.description:
We are Yellow Lab Games, and we're currently working on Metavoidal! A game about a drummer!

Play our alpha build now! It's free on Itch:
https://yellowlabgames.itch.io/metavoidal

Face the music, and the corruption it causes, and try to get out alive by escaping the clutches of the evil Band. 

Join the community:
https://discord.gg/PQ7tpvaRn8

Or follow our social media!
https://twitter.com/YellowLabGames
https://www.instagram.com/yellowlabgames

Thanks for supporting our indie game company.
